Class GraphStructure

java.lang.Object
iscte.se.landmanagement.GraphStructure
public class GraphStructure extends Object
Represents a graph structure for managing and visualizing relationships between properties. Each property is represented as a vertex, and edges are created between vertices if the properties meet a specified adjacency condition.
